          "siteTitle": "New employee corporate onboarding site",
          "siteDescriptor": "Engage and inform new employees",
          "descriptionParagraphs": [
              "Streamline and refine your new employee onboarding process by creating a new employee landing experience that connects new hires to resources, people, culture, and access a new hire onboarding checklist. The Corporate site comes with pre-populated content and pages that can be customized to align with your organization new employee onboarding processes.",
              "Consider using the Pre-onboarding site template and the Departmental onboarding site template to create an end-to-end new hire experience that begins from the day the job offer is accepted and extends beyond general corporate onboarding.",
              "<a href='https://lookbook.microsoft.com/details/8fefcc9a-7ca4-457f-bd10-acee3ae63b63'>Learn more about the Pre-onboarding site</a>.",
              "<a href='https://lookbook.microsoft.com/details/99d3b7ea-6ca0-430e-96bc-922d4d2de2ab'>Learn more about the Departmental onboarding site</a>."
          ],
